Name: Fight Ascending
About the game: This is a fast-paced arcade-style casual fighting game. The levels are all randomly generated by the program and can be challenged forever. Gameplay Go to the next level after completing the objectives of each level. Improve the attributes of the characters as you like. Go back to the upper level after failure.
